Add Drillthrough functionality

For added functionality in our report, we want to utilize drill-through. So when the user clicks on a zip code on the first report page, it will take them to the detailed report page with a page filter for that zip code already in place.

This is done by going into the report page that we want the drill-through to take us to and adding Zip Codes to the Drillthrough option



This automatically creates the functionality as well as adding a "back button" marked in the image below. We can make it easier for the user to see and interact with by formatting the colors. Please note that it could appear over the logo and is hard to see.



Now we can drill-through from Worst & Best Zip Codes by right clicking a zip code value and choose Drill-through
